text: Samsung Galaxy S5, Galaxy S5 or just GS5 is an Android smartphone made by Samsung Electronics. The phone was started on 11 April 2014 in 150 countries as the successor to the Samsung Galaxy S4. Like the Samsung Galaxy S4, the Samsung Galaxy S5 is similar to the prior year model, placing a large focus on a better build with a textured rear cover and IP67 rating for dust and water proof (up to ), a better user feel, new security items such as a fingerprint scanner and private mode, expanded health items (such as a built-in heart rate scanner), and an updated camera. The successor of the Samsung Galaxy S5 is the Samsung Galaxy S6. ==Related pages== * Samsung Galaxy == References == Category:Samsung Galaxy Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2014 Category:Mobile phones with 4K video recording
